    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h1><ol><li>进入目录/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/</li><li>修改ifcfg-enxxxxxxxx 文件  (即你的网卡标识命名的配置文件)</li><li>将ONBOOT=no改成yes</li></ol><p>```<br>cd /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/<br>vim ifcfg-enxxxxxxxx</p><p>//或者</p><p>vim /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-enxxxxxxxx</p>]]></content>
    
